notes.title: Sorrow
notes.content:
I'm feeling deeper in the cycle all i'm feeling is a reaper 
soul slipping every demon untill the mouth of this creature 
I created can't maintain it I just blame it on the demons.
for the reasons can I reason with a man who don't believe me 

Anything anymore for trying all this, i'm feeling fine, just for tonight 
I'm so alone, i'm addictied to, my whole life I spawn the demons and I can't rely

notes.title: BeCarefulUpThere
notes.content:
Free fall death all the way down.
My last scream no one around.
Citics role sound as I touch the ground.
Good bye every little think I found.
I can't breath on my own I need you, more then I ever did.

notes.title: Annotations
Project features
notes.content:
1. Create a project 
2. Link a note category to the project
3. Create up to 5 project board sections.
4. Freely name these sections 
5. Drag and drop 
6. Task count
7. Complete project button
8. Estimated time count


Complete project screen features
1. Tell the user how long it took to complete the project 
2. Tell How many tasks where completed 


Board tasks features
1. Crud opereations 
2. Set a estimated time


Project Object 
1. id : int
2. creationDate : Date
3. name : str
4. desription: str
5. notes : Object
6. board : Object
